examples.en: Mercifully, the professor always makes our tests easy.
Mercifully, I managed to stop the car just in time.
He dealt with the thief mercifully.
His crimes have been dealt with mercifully.
Mercifully, the writer leaves most of the physical horrors to our imagination.
